Get Summary

Source: R/additional_functions.R
get_summary.Rd

Function for creating a short summary of the estimated Iota components.

Usage

get_summary(object)

Arguments

object

An object of class iotarelr_iota2 created by compute_iota2, check_new_rater, or check_dgf.

Value

Prints central statistics of the estimated model.
